<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-68-0173 </DOCNO><TEXT>Gas infrared heaters have been in use in industrial processing and paperindustries for a number of years, mainly in Europe and United States.Interest in infrared drying has increased considerably during the pastfew years. Recent material technology advances have made singinficantheating efficiency improvement. An increase in production capacity from10 to 20% can be reached on paper machines. Finally the infrared canbe used as a total drying system. This can be justified by their highdrying rate and low capital cost investment.</TEXT></DOC>